Articles.Content:
@Greenfire32

Point taken, when I write community I tend to think of the forum community, and like you said I often feel like we're treated as second class citizens. Sure we get the daily kerbal, but that's about it. In general the latest stuff gets posted somewhere else and the feedback here (especially when it contains any sort of criticism) seems to be largely ignored (which is primarily what I meant in terms of Squad ignoring the community).

I really hope that at some point Squad can get their community relations back together, but I'm glad that the forum community is still strong in spite of everything. As far as gaming communities go, this really is one of the best ones I've seen.
